ockquote><br />\n烏龜！<del></del>你唔洗吹雞喇！"},{"pid":"3ba38c2b26a2b377d1e1bf37feb53690f69827f2","tid":295361,"uid":58953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114f67ff992be859293e0c985fdf7feca11e97e9","tid":295361,"uid":58953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47541492f80aa68b0ef82d09e0b798700f723c25","tid":295361,"uid":58953,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:00:49.000Z","msg":"電話都cut埋，facebook名又轉埋，你真係好撚恐怖，當我識錯你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f52accfb8174289d572169c41f92b0ce58c2b51","tid":295361,"uid":68202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d3186432a05d1b54ae7fc07bf386b8a02f68be","tid":295361,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:09:09.000Z","msg":"轉呢啲就話人恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784626834a678fbb26c1986ef4dddfa3c8074d75","tid":295361,"uid":58953,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:20:14.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗做到咁絕咁盡啊，做乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd42c7d966780172d5c27f5038a00eb2cf6e429","tid":295361,"uid":43308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:28:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b78d5a038290d4728f5216bbb5a410385b554c1","tid":295361,"uid":58953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你真係好撚笨柒 <img src=\"/assets/